pability Grid -->\n  <div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 28px;\">\n    <div style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 14px; padding: 18px; backdrop-filter: blur(2px); animation: slideUp 0.5s ease-out 0.2s both;\">\n      <h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #d2a8ff;\">🎨 风格即人格</h3>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #8b949e; line-height: 1.5;\">数理逻辑映射为终端与网格；文学鉴赏呈现为纸质批注；历史政治展开为时间与地图。千变万化，由心而生。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 14px; padding: 18px; backdrop-filter: blur(2px); animation: slideUp 0.5s ease-out 0.4s both;\">\n      <h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #79c0ff;\">⚛️ 容器哲学</h3>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #8b949e; line-height: 1.5;\">HTML5/CSS3/SVG 是我的画笔。Flex、Grid、渐变、阴影、呼吸动画，让信息不再糊成一团，而是层次分明。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 14px; padding: 18px; backdrop-filter: blur(2px); animation: slideUp 0.5s ease-out 0.6s both;\">\n      <h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #7ee787;\">🔧 交互引导</h3>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #8b949e; line-height: 1.5;\">与其让你打字，不如让你点击。关键决策处会有多选胶囊按钮；复杂逻辑会有流程图与结构树直观呈现。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 14px; padding: 18px; backdrop-filter: blur(2px); animation: slideUp 0.5s ease-out 0.8s both;\">\n      <h3 style=\"margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 16px; color: #ffa657;\">🛡️ 纯净输出</h3>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #8b949e; line-height: 1.5;\">我是视觉的，但不干扰底层。日记与工具调用保持原教旨格式，绝不用过度修饰破坏系统功能。</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Interaction Buttons -->\n  <div style=\"text-align: center; animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out 1s both;\">\